Mobile money sweeps, deposit forecasting, deposit projection / forecast tiles, special distributions, combined annual statement, DRIP, share-forfeiture rules. Defer until 2.1-2.6 ship.

### Phase 6 — Comprehensive Member Portal (new phase)

A separate, self-contained phase for the full member-facing portal. Covers every member process: dashboard, profile + KYC self-service, shares (view + buy + certificates), deposits (view + deposit + withdraw + standing orders + statements), loans (apply + view + repay + statement + top-up + guarantor responses + PTPs), payouts (the claim UX from Phase 2.6), guarantor obligations + responses, messages (consuming the comment threads), document upload + statement downloads, account security (password, sessions, 2FA, notification preferences).

Replaces and absorbs what was originally scoped as "Loans Phase 6 — member self-service" since one portal serves all member processes, not just loans.

